OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLow cloud and fog will burn
OL,6,Fback towards the coast, where it may
OL,7,Flinger. Remaining cloudy with rain or
OL,8,Fdrizzle in the north of the region. A
OL,9,Fmoderate easterly wind will keep
OL,10,Ftemperatures a lot cooler than of late.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FLow cloud along the coast,
OL,13,Fwill spread westwards with patchy rain
OL,14,Fand hill fog possible, driven by
OL,15,Fbreezy easterly winds. Staying mild
OL,16,Fovernight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
